The creature comforter requires a daily fee of seafarer's cowries to provide caretaking services, which will be collected at the time of request and then at 1712 p.m.a.m. (Earth time) each day thereafter. Daily fees are only charged once. A team of mammets will administer feed and collect up to 20 leavings per animal. Entrust the creature comforter with care of this animal using the following feed? ※Care will be halted in the following circumstances: 　・Seafarer's cowries are insufficient. 　・Leavings have reached the maximum of 20. ※Care and associated fees will resume automatically once required conditions have been met. ※Leavings collected via the caretaking service will not provide island EXP.
